<CAPTION>  Photos (3); PHOTO: Volcanic ash from Mount Pinatubo caved in the church roof,
above, leaving a debris-filled aisle for the wedding of Lee Sigsworth and
Laura Lyn De Leon on Sunday.; PHOTO: Ash covers trees in Tarlac, at right, and
creates midday darkness on Monday. The volcano, which has erupted every day
for nearly two weeks, spewed ash to 33,000 feet, covering a wide area of Luzon
in the Philippines.; PHOTO: Associated Press; Harlow; PHOTO: Associated Press;
Taxi drivers in Capas, near the erupting mountain, display the latest in
